{{#is_alert}}

## What's happening?
ClickHouse replica delay on {{host.name}} has exceeded the critical threshold over the last 15 minutes. Replicas may be serving stale data.

## How to investigate
Check `system.replicas` for tables with high `absolute_delay`. Look for network issues between replicas, or high write load on the primary shard.

